    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = wp.abs((wp.sin(v0 + 0.92) + v1))
    v1 = (wp.cos(0.65) + wp.cos((v0 + 0.14 * v2 + 0.32)))
    v2 = wp.abs(wp.exp((v0 + 0.07 * v2 + 1.00)))
    v2 = (wp.sin((v0 + 0.91 + tmp + 0.90)) + 0.83)
    data[tid] = v0
